my man ( &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; watashi no otoko ) is a 2014 japanese romantic drama film directed by &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; and based on kazuki sakuraba 's watashi no otoko novel . it was released on 14 june 2014 in japan . the film won the golden george at the 36th moscow international film festival and tadanobu asano won the award for best actor . fumi &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; won international rising star award for this film at new york asian film festival and best actress at 6th tama film awards .